{"tid":2418530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"凌晨12時起可網站預約接種 一開即「跪低」變Error 525","createTime":"2021-02-22T16:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:57:07.000Z","uid":239336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9baee296cdee15730c2097ad9a46f879387eafc8","tid":2418530,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"市民參與程度成疑的武漢肺炎疫苗社區接種計劃，今日展開。雖然政府近日卯足幹勁大力宣傳，符合接種資格的人士今天（23日）就可在網站預約。<br />\n<br />\n踏入23日0時0分，疫苗接種網上預約系統正式開始，但例牌「甩轆」，分別出現Error 521及Error 525，無法連上系統網頁。有市民「排隊成功」，等候約8分鐘，最後仍出現Error 525，無法繼續預約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/46G4D7ZVXNGOHCUMHRODEEOXE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2F46G4D7ZVXNGOHCUMHRODEEOXE4%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=c54b42aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2F46G4D7ZVXNGOHCUMHRODEEOXE4%2F&h=729d8662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/46G4D7ZVXNGOHCUMHRODEEOXE4/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6003194b83eb9dffee740836728050c16d0ab6d9","tid":2418530,"uid":276887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"以為講緊bno"},{"pid":"a73122db294cac6ceadff056e1cbb161262936d2","tid":2418530,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"又有中非網友book呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b15f6ca8cb8f8b261d99ff2be874ea7d04be6c","tid":2418530,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"扮多人預約<i